[5.089321, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m\ud83d\udd27 ADK MCP Setup\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nGive your coding agent the power to build and deploy ADK projects.\r\n\r\n  \ud83d\udcda Browse and search ADK codebase knowledge\r\n  \ud83d\ude80 Go from prototype to production\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n\r  \u280b Detecting coding agents"]
[5.146206, "o", "\r                           \r\u001b[1mAgents\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2713 Claude Code     (configured)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2713 Gemini CLI      (configured)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2713 Cursor          (configured)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m    Windsurf        (not detected)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2713 Antigravity     (configured)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m    Codex           (not detected)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m    Roo Code        (not detected)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mConfigure\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Claude Code (already configured \u2014 update?) [y/N]: "]
[5.646206, "o", "y"]
[5.902631, "o", "\r\n  Gemini CLI (already configured \u2014 update?) [y/N]: "]
[6.203098, "o", "y"]
[6.446389, "o", "\r\n  Cursor (already configured \u2014 update?) [y/N]: "]
[6.74818, "o", "y"]
[7.103495, "o", "\r\n  Antigravity (already configured \u2014 update?) [y/N]: "]
[7.417587, "o", "y"]
[7.729316, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mConfiguration to be applied (MCP + skills):\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  Claude Code\u001b[0m\r\n  -> /Users/developer/.claude.json\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  Gemini CLI\u001b[0m\r\n  -> /Users/developer/.gemini/settings.json\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  Cursor\u001b[0m\r\n  -> /Users/developer/.cursor/mcp.json\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  Antigravity\u001b[0m\r\n  -> /Users/developer/.gemini/antigravity/mcp_config.json\r\n\r\n  Proceed with configuration [Y/n]: "]
[8.229316, "o", "y"]
[8.5171, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2705 Claude Code \u2014 MCP server + skills configured\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2705 Gemini CLI \u2014 MCP server + skills configured\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2705 Cursor \u2014 MCP server + skills configured\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  \u2705 Antigravity \u2014 MCP server + skills configured\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n\u001b[32m\u001b[1m\ud83c\udf89 Setup complete!\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mNext steps:\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  1. Run 'claude' in your terminal, Run 'gemini' in your terminal, Open Cursor app or Open Antigravity IDE\r\n  2. Start a new conversation\r\n  3. Try: \"Help me build a document search agent with ADK\"\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mWhat was configured:\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  MCP server    Knowledge base search, symbol inspection, project scaffolding\r\n  Skills        Copied from package\r\n\r\n  Available skills:\r\n    /adk-cheatsheet     ADK API patterns and code examples\r\n    /adk-dev-guide       Development lifecycle and coding guidelines\r\n    /adk-eval-guide      Evaluation methodology and gotchas\r\n    /adk-deploy-guide    Deployment and CI/CD setup\r\n\r\n\u001b[2m  Run 'adk mcp config' for manual JSON configuration.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
